Detailed Description

Class for holding information about a token.

When packed into or from a packet UserToken looks like this. The first TYPE and Total size in bytes and the last TYPE is read by someone else when read from a packet. {tabular}{lll} Pos & Size & Destription \ pos & 4 bytes & TYPE_TOKEN \ +4 & 2 bytes & Total size in bytes \ +6 & 4 bytes & TYPE_TOKEN \ +10 & 2 bytes & Total size in bytes \ +12 & 4 bytes & ID \ +16 & 4 bytes & Creation time. \ +20 & 1 bytes & The number of tokens before this that has used the AC. \ +21 & string & The token. {tabular}
